THE KILMOREY COINCIDENCE
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    When two similar or linked events occur at the same time it is a
    coincidence. When three similar or linked events occur at the same
    time it is unusual and strange. When three similar or linked events
    occur at the same time within an environment that already has a
    lurking reputation for weirdness then you had better start thinking
    of calling Ghostbusters... and so it was on Sunday 18th September.

