EVENT: ENVIRONMENT TRUST ART AUCTION - 17 NOVEMBER 2016
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    The Environment Trust has been running an annual Art Auction
    for many years. It is a very popular local event and a major
    fund-raiser, helping to support the work we do. The theme for the
    2016 auction will be _Working Lives, Working Places_ to complement
    one of the Trust's new projects which the proceeds of the auction
    will support.

